<hymn_number>236</hymn_number>
<title>Van Jerusalem Thak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mel muh phak loh van Jerusalem thak,
 Angel leh Zuo Minlun laituol lenna;
 Tik leh lei gimna taihsan in ka tung dem,
 Thangvan khawlun Lalpa vangkhaw sat thak?

[V2]
 Nuoi simlei gamthipa ka len lai hin,
 Vangkhaw lunlai ngaiin ka mau;
 Mu bang ka ngaih vangkhaw nuom chu,
 Tik leh thuongte ka tung dei mawh?

[V3]
 2. Lalpa ngaia nau bang kahna gam hi,
 Albang mang hen lungkhamna nuoi simlei
 Albang dahna mei zing nuoi a hin Lalpa
 Na sakmel kipahum ei muhsak in.

[V4]
 3. Lungkhamna dahna dawn bang ka tuok nin
 Lungkham puong ie Minlun Lal vangin
 &quot;Lau kin, ngaiin hun veng zing ingka&quot; A tii.
 Ei hehpihna tawngka nemtak mai chun

[V5]
 4. Thihna Jordan luipi ka kan ding tieng,
 Lalpan a khut lopi'n ei pui in tin,
 Lung lau loa Jordan luipi ka kan tieng,
 Lalpa vangkhaw thakah ngabang leng ka.</lyrics>
</song>